<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Kampung Naga</title>
  <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com/3.4.17"></script>
  <!-- Lucide Icons -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lucide@0.263.0/dist/umd/lucide.min.js"></script>
  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Alegreya:wght@400;500;700;800&family=Alegreya+Sans:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    :root { --vh: 1vh; }
    body { font-family: 'Alegreya Sans', sans-serif; }
    h1, h2, h3, h4 { font-family: 'Alegreya', serif; }
    .hero-overlay { background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(15,23,42,0.6) 0%, rgba(15,23,42,0.3) 50%, rgba(15,23,42,0.8) 100%); }
    .capacity-pulse { animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
    @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.4; } }
    .card-hover { transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; }
    .card-hover:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
    .fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out forwards; opacity: 0; }
    @keyframes fadeIn { to { opacity: 1; } }
    .stagger-1 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .stagger-2 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .stagger-3 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="w-full min-h-screen bg-stone-50 text-stone-800">

  <!-- NAVIGATION -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-stone-900/95 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-stone-700">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 flex items-center justify-between h-14">
      <a href="#beranda" class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-400 tracking-wide">Kampung Naga</a>
      <div class="hidden md:flex gap-6 text-sm">
        <a href="#beranda" class="text-stone-300 hover:text-emerald-400 transition">Beranda</a>
        <a href="#virtual" class="text-stone-300 hover:text-emerald-400 transition">Naga Virtual</a>
        <a href="#booking" class="text-stone-300 hover:text-emerald-400 transition">Pesan Kunjungan</a>
        <a href="#panduan" class="text-stone-300 hover:text-emerald-400 transition">Panduan Adat</a>
        <a href="#kriya" class="text-stone-300 hover:text-emerald-400 transition">Kriya Naga</a>
      </div>
      <button id="mobile-menu-btn" class="md:hidden text-stone-300 focus:outline-none">
        <i data-lucide="menu" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
    <!-- Mobile Menu Container -->
    <div id="mobile-menu" class="hidden md:hidden bg-stone-900 border-t border-stone-800 px-4 py-3 space-y-2 animate-fadeIn">
      <a href="#beranda" class="block text-stone-300 hover:text-emerald-400 py-1 transition">Beranda</a>
      <a href="#virtual" class="block text-stone-300 hover:text-emerald-400 py-1 transition">Naga Virtual</a>
      <a href="#booking" class="block text-stone-300 hover:text-emerald-400 py-1 transition">Pesan Kunjungan</a>
      <a href="#panduan" class="block text-stone-300 hover:text-emerald-400 py-1 transition">Panduan Adat</a>
      <a href="#kriya" class="block text-stone-300 hover:text-emerald-400 py-1 transition">Kriya Naga</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section id="beranda" class="relative w-full min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
    <img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1547429/pexels-photo-1547429.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1920" alt="Pemandangan sawah dan pedesaan tradisional Sunda">
    <div class="hero-overlay absolute inset-0"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mt-12">
      <h1 class="text-white text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold drop-shadow-lg fade-in">Kampung Naga</h1>
      <p class="text-stone-200 text-lg md:text-xl mt-4 max-w-2xl优化 fade-in stagger-1">
        Jelajahi warisan budaya Sunda yang autentik — 444 anak tangga menuju peradaban yang menjaga tradisi leluhur sejak ratusan tahun silam.
      </p>

      <!-- Capacity Monitor UI Component -->
      <div class="mt-8 bg-stone-900/80 backdrop-blur border border-stone-700/50 rounded-2xl p-6 max-w-md w-full fade-in stagger-2 shadow-2xl">
        <p class="text-stone-400 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 font-semibold">Sistem Kendali Daya Tampung (Live)</p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <span id="traffic-light" class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-green-500 capacity-pulse"></span>
          <span id="visitor-count" class="text-4xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">284</span>
          <span class="text-stone-500 text-xl">/ 500</span>
        </div>
        <p id="capacity-status" class="text-emerald-400 text-sm mt-2 font-medium">Kondisi Aman: Sisa kuota masuk fisik hari ini tersedia.</p>
      </div>

      <a href="#booking" class="mt-8 inline-block bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-full transition duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-emerald-900/40 fade-in stagger-3">
        Reservasi Kunjungan Langsung
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NAGA VIRTUAL SECTION -->
  <section id="virtual" class="w-full py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-stone-800 text-center mb-4">Naga Virtual (Wisata Inklusif)</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 text-base md:text-lg">
        Gerbang digital ramah aksesibilitas. Didesain khusus agar para lansia, anak-anak, dan penyandang disabilitas dapat menikmati keunikan adat tanpa hambatan medan fisik.
      </p>

      <!-- Virtual Tour Previews -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md bg-white card-hover border border-stone-200">
          <div class="relative group cursor-pointer" onclick="alert('Membuka Fitur Simulasi Kamera Virtual 360° Anak Tangga...')">
            <img class="w-full h-64 object-cover" loading="lazy" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/21952599/pexels-photo-21952599.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Anak tangga kayu di area hijau rindang">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 flex items-center justify-center transition duration-300">
              <span class="bg-white/90 text-stone-900 px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                <i data-lucide="eye" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Mulai Tur 360°
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Simulasi 444 Anak Tangga</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Rasakan sensasi panorama visual menuruni lembah sungai Ci Wulan menuju gerbang desa adat secara imersif dan interaktif.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md bg-white card-hover border border-stone-200">
          <div class="relative group cursor-pointer" onclick="alert('Membuka Fitur Kamera Interaktif Interior Sanubari Adat...')">
            <img class="w-full h-64 object-cover" loading="lazy" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/8178023/pexels-photo-8178023.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Bangunan rumah panggung bambu tradisional">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 flex items-center justify-center transition duration-300">
              <span class="bg-white/90 text-stone-900 px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                <i data-lucide="eye" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Lihat Arsitektur
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Arsitektur Rumah Sanubari</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Pelajari detail arsitektur rumah panggung anyaman bambu beratap ijuk yang dirancang seragam dan tanpa paku bangunan.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Audio Book Player Component -->
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-800 text-center mb-8">Audio Book — Rekaman Narasi Kebudayaan</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Audio Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-stone-200 card-hover">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <button class="audio-btn w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-md transition duration-200" data-audio="audio1">
              <i data-lucide="play" class="w-5 h-5 ml-0.5 btn-icon"></i>
            </button>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-stone-900 text-lg">Upacara Hajat Sasih</h4>
          </div>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Eksplorasi audio mengenai ritus rutin pembersihan makam leluhur dan ungkapan rasa syukur kolektif masyarakat adat Naga.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Audio Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-stone-200 card-hover">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <button class="audio-btn w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-md transition duration-200" data-audio="audio2">
              <i data-lucide="play" class="w-5 h-5 ml-0.5 btn-icon"></i>
            </button>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-stone-900 text-lg">Kedaulatan Agraris</h4>
          </div>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Kisah harian pola hidup mandiri: cara bercocok tanam organik terintegrasi, menumbuk padi manual, dan kerajinan anyam.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Audio Card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-stone-200 card-hover">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <button class="audio-btn w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-md transition duration-200" data-audio="audio3">
              <i data-lucide="play" class="w-5 h-5 ml-0.5 btn-icon"></i>
            </button>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-stone-900 text-lg">Kaulinan Lembur</h4>
          </div>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Kumpulan rekaman suara keceriaan permainan egrang, congklak, dan kolecer bambu yang lestari melintasi generasi.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Ambient Soundscape Player Section -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden h-48 group cursor-pointer shadow" onclick="alert('Memutar Efek Suara Ambient Sungai Ci Wulan...')">
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-105" loading="lazy" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1005472/pexels-photo-1005472.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Aliran sungai jernih di dekat hutan">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-950/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex items-end p-6">
            <p class="text-white font-medium flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="volume-2" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400"></i> Soundscape: Gemercik Air Sungai Ci Wulan</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden h-48 group cursor-pointer shadow" onclick="alert('Memutar Efek Suara Angin dan Serangga Sawah...')">
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-105" loading="lazy" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/13013188/pexels-photo-13013188.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Sawah hijau nan asri">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-950/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex items-end p-6">
            <p class="text-white font-medium flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="volume-2" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400"></i> Soundscape: Desau Angin & Harpa Sawah</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BOOKING SECTION -->
  <section id="booking" class="w-full py-20 px-4 bg-stone-100 border-y border-stone-200">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-stone-800 text-center mb-4">Pesan Kunjungan & Homestay (OTA)</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        Sistem manajemen kunjungan terpadu. Seluruh kontribusi biaya penginapan dan pemandu lokal dialokasikan 100% langsung untuk kemaslahatan warga.
      </p>

      <!-- Homestay List Grid -->
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="home" class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600"></i> Homestay Warga Asli</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white card-hover border border-stone-200">
          <img class="w-full h-48 object-cover" loading="lazy" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2058752/pexels-photo-2058752.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Kamar interior kayu hangat">
          <div class="p-5">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-stone-900 text-lg">Saung Hejo</h4>
            <p class="text-emerald-700 font-bold mt-1 text-base">Rp 150.000 / malam</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-2">Gubuk panggung bambu estetik di bibir terasering sawah. Ideal untuk 2-3 orang.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white card-hover border border-stone-200">
          <img class="w-full h-48 object-cover" loading="lazy" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/271649/pexels-photo-271649.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Ruangan minimalis beralas anyaman mat">
          <div class="p-5">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-stone-900 text-lg">Imah Bambu</h4>
            <p class="text-emerald-700 font-bold mt-1 text-base">Rp 200.000 / malam</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-2">Struktur panggung tradisional dengan ruang tengah lapang, pas untuk liburan keluarga kecil.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white card-hover border border-stone-200">
          <img class="w-full h-48 object-cover" loading="lazy" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/12326545/pexels-photo-12326545.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Jendela kayu sederhana menghadap pepohonan">
          <div class="p-5">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-stone-900 text-lg">Pondok Adat</h4>
            <p class="text-emerald-700 font-bold mt-1 text-base">Rp 175.000 / malam</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-2">Merasakan ritme otentik bermukim seraya berinteraksi hangat dengan keseharian empunya rumah.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Local Guides Guide Grid -->
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="users" class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600"></i> Pemandu Lokal</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="flex gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-stone-200 card-hover">
          <img class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-emerald-500/20" loading="lazy" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/36732027/pexels-photo-36732027.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" alt="Wajah kakek bijak berpakaian adat">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-stone-900">Abah Eman</h4>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Tetua adat karismatik dengan wawasan mendalam kisah historiografi tutur Kampung Naga selama lebih dari 40 tahun.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-stone-200 card-hover">
          <img class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-emerald-500/20" loading="lazy" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/17403554/pexels-photo-17403554.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" alt="Pemuda tani ramah tersenyum">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-stone-900">Kang Asep</h4>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Pemandu muda enerjik bilingual (Sunda-Indonesia), pakar pendamping rute agrowisata dan lokakarya kerajinan.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Booking Form Component -->
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 border border-stone-200/60">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-6 text-center">Formulir Reservasi Digital</h3>
        <form id="booking-form" class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <label for="visitor-name" class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 block mb-1">Nama Lengkap</label>
            <input id="visitor-name" type="text" required class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 focus:border-emerald-500 outline-none transition" placeholder="Masukkan nama Anda">
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div>
              <label for="visitor-email" class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 block mb-1">Email</label>
              <input id="visitor-email" type="email" required class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 focus:border-emerald-500 outline-none transition" placeholder="email@contoh.com">
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="visitor-phone" class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 block mb-1">Nomor Telepon</label>
              <input id="visitor-phone" type="tel" required class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 focus:border-emerald-500 outline-none transition" placeholder="08xxxxxxxxxx">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div>
              <label for="visit-date" class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 block mb-1">Tanggal Kunjungan</label>
              <input id="visit-date" type="date" required class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 focus:border-emerald-500 text-stone-600 outline-none transition">
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="num-visitors" class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 block mb-1">Jumlah Pengunjung</label>
              <input id="num-visitors" type="number" min="1" max="20" value="1" required class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 focus:border-emerald-500 outline-none transition">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="homestay-select" class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 block mb-1">Pilih Homestay (Opsional)</label>
            <select id="homestay-select" class="w-full border border-stone-300 bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 text-stone-600 outline-none transition">
              <option value="">Tidak perlu menginap</option>
              <option value="homestay-1">Saung Hejo - Rp 150.000/malam</option>
              <option value="homestay-2">Imah Bambu - Rp 200.000/malam</option>
              <option value="homestay-3">Pondok Adat - Rp 175.000/malam</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="guide-select" class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 block mb-1">Pilih Pemandu (Opsional)</label>
            <select id="guide-select" class="w-full border border-stone-300 bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 text-stone-600 outline-none transition">
              <option value="">Tanpa pemandu lokal</option>
              <option value="guide-1">Abah Eman (Sesepuh Adat)</option>
              <option value="guide-2">Kang Asep (Pemandu Muda)</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg transition duration-200 mt-2 shadow-md">
            Kirim Formulir Reservasi
          </button>
        </form>

        <!-- Status Form Handlers -->
        <div id="form-loading" class="hidden text-center py-4">
          <div class="inline-block w-6 h-6 border-2 border-emerald-600 border-t-transparent rounded-full animate-spin"></div>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mt-2">Memproses kuota & mencatat jadwal...</p>
        </div>
        <div id="form-success" class="hidden text-center py-6">
          <i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-12 h-12 text-emerald-600 mx-auto mb-3"></i>
          <p class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg">Reservasi Berhasil Diajukan!</p>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Kode booking dan detail akomodasi telah dikirim ke email & WhatsApp Anda.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PANDUAN ADAT SECTION -->
  <section id="panduan" class="w-full py-20 px-4 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-stone-800 text-center mb-4">Etika & Panduan Adat</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        Teknologi hadir untuk melindungi keaslian adat, bukan mengikisnya. Mohon patuhi aturan fundamental berikut saat melakukan kunjungan fisik.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check-square" class="w-5 h-5"></i> Yang Harus Dilakukan (Do's)</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm md:text-base">
            <li class="bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-stone-700 flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold">✓</span> Berpakaian sopan, tertutup rapi, dan berperilaku santun selama di kawasan pemukiman.
            </li>
            <li class="bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-stone-700 flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold">✓</span> Wajib meminta izin terlebih dahulu kepada pemandu sebelum mendokumentasikan warga.
            </li>
            <li class="bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-stone-700 flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold">✓</span> Menjaga keasrian, ketenangan alam, dan membawa kembali sampah pribadi ke luar desa.
            </li>
          </ul>
